<section id="contacto" class="contact-section">
  <h2>Contacto</h2>
  <p>¿Tienes alguna pregunta o comentario? Contáctanos a través del formulario o<br>llámanos al <a href="tel:+525512345678">+52 55 1234 5678</a>.</p>
  <form>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="name">Nombre</label>
      <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Ingresa tu nombre">
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="email">Correo Electrónico</label>
      <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Ingresa tu correo electrónico">
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="message">Mensaje</label>
      <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Escribe tu mensaje"></textarea>
    </div>
    <button type="submit" class="button">Enviar</button>
  </form>
</section>

<style>
  .contact-section {
    background-color: #F9F5F2;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .contact-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .contact-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .contact-section a {
    color: #E67E22;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .contact-section form {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .contact-section .form-group {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .contact-section label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #333;
  }
  .contact-section input,
  .contact-section textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 1rem;
    background-color: #fff;
  }
  .contact-section .button {
    background-color: #E67E22;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    display: inline-block;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 1rem;
    width: auto;
  }
</style>